<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">宸恩</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">清高宗</cb:mulu>
<milestone unit="juan" n="2"/>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0015a" n="0015a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a01"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="2"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="2"><cb:jhead>增修雲林寺志卷二</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a02"/><byline cb:type="collector">錢塘厲鶚太鴻增輯</byline>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a03"/><byline cb:type="collector">仁和張熷曦亮同輯</byline>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a04"/><byline cb:type="other">住持義果巨濤參訂</byline>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">山水</cb:mulu><head>山水</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">武林山</cb:mulu><head>武林山</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0015a0604" cb:place="inline">漢書地理志會稽郡錢塘注武林山武林水
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a07"/>所出祥符圖經云在縣西十五里高九十二丈周
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a08"/>廻一十二里又曰靈隱曰靈苑曰仙居也又按十
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a09"/>三州記云武林山高九十二丈周廻三十里在錢
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a10"/>塘縣西南十二里靈隱寺正坐其山寺之東西瀵
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0016a" n="0016a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a01"/>二水東龍源橫過寺前<reg>即</reg>龍溪也冷泉亭在其上
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a02"/>西曰錢源其流洪大下山二里八十步過橫坑橋
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a03"/>入於錢湖蓋錢源之聚滀也</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">稽留峰</cb:mulu><head>稽留峰</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0016a0404" cb:place="inline">太平寰宇記云許由葛洪皆隱此山忘返故
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a05"/>號稽留</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">理公巖</cb:mulu><head>理公巖</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0016a0604" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在靈鷲院之右陸羽寺記云
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a07"/>昔慧理宴息於下後有僧於巖上周囘鐫小羅漢
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a08"/>佛菩薩像慈雲法師所謂訪慧理之禪巖弔客兒
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a09"/>之山館是也近主僧行果始作閣道屬之巖中以
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a10"/>祠理公</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0017a" n="0017a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">白猿峰</cb:mulu><head>白猿峰</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0017a0104" cb:place="inline">遵式白猿峰詩序云西僧慧理蓄白猿於靈
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a02"/>隱寺詩云引水穿廊走呼猿繞澗跳</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">龍泓洞</cb:mulu><head>龍<reg>泓</reg>洞</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0017a0304" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在理公巖之北晏元獻公云
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a04"/>吳赤烏二年葛仙翁於此得道後有人就洞兩岸
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a05"/>鑿住世羅漢十六尊</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">玉女巖</cb:mulu><head>玉女巖</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0017a0604" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云太平寰宇記靈隱山南一石
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a07"/>狀似人形兩髻分明俗謂之女兒山顧野王地志
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a08"/>云靈隱山南有玉女巖</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">葛塢</cb:mulu><head>葛塢</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0017a0903" cb:place="inline">晏元獻公輿地志云在靈隱山吳方士葛孝先
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a10"/>所居也陸羽寺記云晉葛洪亦居此</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0018a" n="0018a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">臥犀泉</cb:mulu><head>臥犀泉</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0018a0104" cb:place="inline">按鄭戩靈隱天竺詩集序云若夫玉巖<reg>青</reg>璧
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a02"/>犀泉龍瀃峰攅千曡松排萬蓋山之境也據此則
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a03"/><reg>青</reg>璧澗臥犀泉皆在靈隱天竺之間</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">白沙泉</cb:mulu><head>白沙泉</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0018a0404" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在靈隱寺西普園院方丈之
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a05"/>西有泉自白沙中出</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">茯苓泉</cb:mulu><head>茯苓泉</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0018a0604" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在靈隱西無垢院半山古松
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a07"/>婆娑下有甘泉博物志云松脂入地千年化為茯
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a08"/>苓因名</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">石人嶺</cb:mulu><head>石人嶺</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0018a0904" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云一名馮公嶺在靈隱寺西極
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a10"/>高峻有石人臥路傍故名</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0019a" n="0019a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">蓮花泉</cb:mulu><head>蓮花泉</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0019a0104" cb:place="inline">在飛來峰頂石巖無土<reg>清</reg>可啜茶見陳善杭
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a02"/>州府志</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">梵宇</cb:mulu><head>梵宇</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0019a0401">大殿　天王殿　地藏殿　伽藍殿　金光明殿
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a05"/>　祖師殿</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0019a0601">法堂　東禪堂　西禪堂　嫩桂堂　南鑑堂　齋
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a07"/>堂　雲水堂　擇木堂　大悲堂　官客堂　直
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a08"/>指堂　法壽堂　羅漢堂</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">閣</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0019a0901">指南閣　聯燈閣　華嚴閣　<reg>青</reg>蓮閣</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">軒</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0019a1001"><reg>青</reg>猊軒　面壁軒
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0020a" n="0020a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a01"/>駐蹕軒</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">樓</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0020a0201">鄉水樓　看月樓　鐘樓</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寮</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0020a0301">公務寮　浴寮　茶寮　打掃寮　值作寮　知器
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a04"/>寮　尊宿寮　山寮</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">亭</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pGA024p0020a0501">冷泉亭</p>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a06"/><p xml:id="pGA024p0020a0601">以上俱乾隆七年新安汪光祿諱應庚<reg>暨</reg>子甯波
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a07"/>府知府諱起同本山住持僧義果重修</p>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a08"/><p xml:id="pGA024p0020a0801">輪藏殿　梵香閣　春淙亭　延壽堂　庫房　總
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a09"/>管堂</p>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a10"/><p xml:id="pGA024p0020a1001">以上俱重建</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0021a" n="0021a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">古蹟</cb:mulu><head>古蹟</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">袁君亭</cb:mulu><head>袁君亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0021a0204" cb:place="inline">陸羽寺記刺史袁仁敬造</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">翠微亭</cb:mulu><head>翠微亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0021a0304" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云紹興十三年韓蘄王世忠建
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a04"/>後廢乾道五年周安撫淙重建</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">石橋亭</cb:mulu><head>石橋亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0021a0504" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在武林山中路近翻經臺</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">月桂亭</cb:mulu><head>月桂亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0021a0604" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在月桂峰下</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">靈山海會之閣</cb:mulu><head>靈山海會之閣</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0021a0707" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在靈鷲寺湻祐十二
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a08"/>年理宗御書扁</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">普圓院</cb:mulu><head>普圓院</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0021a0904" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云天福二年吳越王建舊名資
<lb ed="GA" n="0021a10"/>嚴大中祥符元年改今額古跡有石筍白沙泉鄴
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0022a" n="0022a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a01"/>公菴</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">法安院</cb:mulu><head>法安院</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0022a0204" cb:place="inline">咸湻臨安志云在靈隱寺西天福三年吳越
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a03"/>王建舊額廣嚴唐長慶中有詩僧結庵於院之西
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a04"/>自號韜光常與樂天唱和大中祥符元年攺今額</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">巢雲亭</cb:mulu><head>巢雲亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0022a0504" cb:place="inline">在寺內見咸湻臨安志</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">徐奭墓</cb:mulu><head>徐奭墓</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0022a0604" cb:place="inline">在靈隱山石筍院徽宗朝賜號冲晦先生</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">慕容妃墓</cb:mulu><head>慕容妃墓</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0022a0705" cb:place="inline">在九里松唐家衕東</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">周殿撰杞墓</cb:mulu><head>周殿撰<note n="0022a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">杞【CB】，<g ref="#CB23780"/>【志彙】</note><app n="0022a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">杞</lem><rdg wit="【志彙】"><g ref="#CB23780"/></rdg></app>墓</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0022a0807" cb:place="inline">在九里松水岡塢咸湻臨安志云<note n="0022a0802" resp="CBETA" type="add">杞【CB】，<g ref="#CB23780"/>【志彙】</note><app n="0022a0802"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">杞</lem><rdg wit="【志彙】"><g ref="#CB23780"/></rdg></app>建
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a09"/>炎三年知常州值苗劉之亂倡義勤王以功除右
<lb ed="GA" n="0022a10"/>文殿修撰</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0023a" n="0023a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">曲水亭</cb:mulu><head>曲水亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0023a0104" cb:place="inline">舊在香林洞側一曰流杯亭有水臺盤為梅
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a02"/>詢靈隱十詠之一</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">將軍教場墓</cb:mulu><head>將軍<reg>教</reg>場墓</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0023a0306" cb:place="inline">在行春橋水竹塢內俗呼唐三寶墓紹
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a04"/>興末因廣<reg>教</reg>場此冡獨高大眾欲去之方舉鍤間
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a05"/>有黑蜂數百飛出不可向是夜戎帥夢一人高冠
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a06"/>朱衣曰吾錢王之子葬此已久祈勿毁方怪之詰
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a07"/>朝得本軍申遂留此墓</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">靈隱天竺寺門</cb:mulu><head>靈隱天竺寺門</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0023a0807" cb:place="inline">在飛來峰牌門東俗呼二寺門又名
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a09"/>方外門慶厯八年太常博士元居中書扁知杭州
<lb ed="GA" n="0023a10"/>府蔣堂立至今不易</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0024a" n="0024a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">密因閣</cb:mulu><head>密因閣</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0024a0104" cb:place="inline">在廻龍橋萬厯辛亥方伯浮渡吳公捐俸建
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a02"/>橋亭題曰覺路津梁上供準提佛題曰密因閣又
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a03"/>為複閣曲軒以對溪流扁枕石潄流</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">方等懺堂</cb:mulu><head>方等懺堂</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0024a0405" cb:place="inline">在寺內萬厯壬子介如石公講楞嚴義海
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a05"/>于寺尋葺此堂集三學精通禪者修方等懺法</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">石佛菴</cb:mulu><head>石佛菴</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0024a0604" cb:place="inline">在靈隱山直指堂後梁簡文帝所造迦葉維
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a07"/>衞石佛二尊萬厯間僧如<g ref="#CB33539"/>持準提咒夢披荒莽
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a08"/>中見石佛像身如芒刺募貲建菴菴後建準提閣
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a09"/>前後皆竹湯煥書竹林精舍</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0024a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">錢和墓</cb:mulu><head>錢和墓</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0024a1004" cb:place="inline">在天竺靈隱西兩山之間吳越王之後仕至
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0025a" n="0025a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a01"/>直秘閣知荊南府</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">忠勇廟</cb:mulu><head>忠勇廟</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0025a0204" cb:place="inline">在九里松祀宋統制張玘</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">超然臺</cb:mulu><head>超然臺</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0025a0304" cb:place="inline">在石筍普圓院內方丈左右金漆板扉皆趙
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a04"/><reg>清</reg>獻諸賢蘇秦陳黃留題及文與可竹數枝如張
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a05"/>揔得父子吳傳朋等題字甚多歲久暗淡猶隱隱
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a06"/>可見</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">宋理宗貴妃閻氏欑宮</cb:mulu><head>宋理宗貴妃閻氏欑<reg>宮</reg></head><p xml:id="pGA024p0025a0710" cb:place="inline">在顯慈集慶寺寺地舊屬靈
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a08"/>隱</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">隆親永福院</cb:mulu><head>隆親永福院</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0025a0906" cb:place="inline">宋温國陳夫人香火今廢永福寺隆國
<lb ed="GA" n="0025a10"/>黃夫人功德咸湻九年建俱在靈隱寺西</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0026a" n="0026a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">宜對亭</cb:mulu><head>宜對亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0026a0104" cb:place="inline">在九里松葉紹翁書見名勝志</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">月波亭</cb:mulu><head>月波亭</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0026a0204" cb:place="inline">靈隱遺事云大松數圍正與月波亭對</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">錢塘縣舊治</cb:mulu><head>錢塘縣舊治</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0026a0306" cb:place="inline">水經注云浙江東逕靈隱山山下有錢
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a04"/>塘故縣</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">杏園</cb:mulu><head>杏園</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0026a0503" cb:place="inline">堯山堂外紀云錢塘莫維賢居靈竺間繞舍栽
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a06"/>杏號曰杏園</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">白閣</cb:mulu><head>白閣</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0026a0703" cb:place="inline">錢塘舊志云明邵重生古菴建白閣於靈鷲山
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a08"/>呼猿洞祀許由及唐宋名賢為樓三楹中祀其父
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a09"/>經邦足不入城市遇節序祭祀歸家信宿已<reg>即</reg>還
<lb ed="GA" n="0026a10"/>山如是者二十年</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA024.0022.0027a" n="0027a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">附錄</cb:mulu><head>附錄</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">湯莊</cb:mulu><head>湯莊</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0027a0203" cb:place="inline">在靈隱寺西舊為明副使包涵所別墅原名<reg>青</reg>
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a03"/>蓮山房倚蓮華峰跨曲澗臺榭之美冠絕一時外
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a04"/>以石屑砌墻柴根編<reg>戶</reg>內則曲房密室行其中者
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a05"/>宛轉不能<reg>即</reg>出今猶稱包氏北莊為前少宰湯公
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a06"/>右曾別業自題有蓮峰紫翠看皆好喬木風烟畫
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a07"/>不如之句</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">白雲山房</cb:mulu><head>白雲山房</head><p xml:id="pGA024p0027a0805" cb:place="inline">在飛來峰之西白雲峰下為副使翁公嵩
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a09"/>年建中有愛吾廬得樹軒環山樓流泉繞屋嵐翠
<lb ed="GA" n="0027a10"/>在庭多植梅桂松竹剝啄罕到習靜最宜</p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
